paragraphs":["<em>Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.</em>","The first thing you&#39;ll notice about the Losi Micro-Desert Truck is its compact size. Measuring only about 6 inches in length, it&#39;s the smallest RC truck that we reviewed. Although it&#39;s small on size, it&#39;s not small on features, and its compact design allows it go places that other hobby-grade trucks simply cannot.","For such a small RC monster truck, this vehicle is extraordinarily fast. A rechargeable NiMH battery powers the truck, and it comes with a portable charger. Unfortunately, the battery-charger requires eight AA batteries, so you&#39;ll have to replace those when they run out. Losi does offer battery upgrades that offer more speed, longer run times and plug-in wall chargers.","Its smaller size means it runs indoors much more easily than other <a href=\"/best-remote-control-cars\">RC car</a> options, but it&#39;ll have a much more difficult time in precarious outdoor terrain. For this reason, it&#39;s better to buy this car as a primarily indoor option.","The Micro-Desert truck comes ready to run, with no additional assembly needed. If you&#39;d like to customize your truck, however, Losi offers extensive part support for this RC car. Not only can you replace broken or misshapen parts, you can upgrade most of its components, as well.","The remote that comes with your Micro-Desert Truck is a 27MHz pistol-grip transmitter. This transmitter requires a whopping eight AA batteries for operation. Luckily, Losi includes those with the vehicle. Navigation is precise, with proportional control over both the throttle and steering of the truck. This means that small adjustments on the controls translate to small adjustments in the truck. This grants the finesse required to drive such a fast indoor truck.","There&#39;s no real warranty included with this truck, although if it&#39;s broken when you pull it out of the box, Losi will repair or replace it for you. According to the user manual, this guarantee only covers you for the exact date of purchase. Fortunately, replacement parts are very easy to find from both Losi and third party dealers. Losi also offers parts lists, downloadable manuals as well as contact information on their website."]},"id":"d4e04ecd-4c82-4045-8b54-4b55fd08da7c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"e510f4ae-b3f1-4ffc-a97f-1f55adc33690","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Losi Micro-Desert Truck is an off-road style truck with realistic looks and hobby-grade features. Although there is no extended warranty with this truck, readily available replacement parts make it easy to keep it running. Its compact dimensions keep it from being a capable off-roading vehicle, but that&#39;s not its primary purpose anyway. Losi designed the Micro-Desert Truck as a convenient, indoor radio controlled car that lets you get your RC fix without ever leaving the house."]},"id":"0542585a-84cb-4582-8a04-3ad1bc8b3bb3","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_57289","url":"/micro-desert-truck-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"caleb-cross","url":"/author/caleb-cross","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Caleb Cross","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"MG9CFuiZaQn2UkqAVvekK9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2013-08-26T14:02:34Z","datePublished":"2013-08-26T14:02:34Z","name":"Micro Desert Truck","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued. You can still read our original review below, but Top Ten Reviews is no longer updating this product’s information.","review":{"rating":63,"verdict":"The Micro-Desert Truck isn&#039;t the most versatile RC truck, but it excels 